sequenceDiagram
  actor C as Client
  participant UI as Front Client
  participant API as API Node
  participant SQL as Base SQL
  participant SMTP as Service SMTP

  C->>UI: Saisie commande
  UI->>API: POST /api/orders
  API->>SQL: Verifie menu/stock/minimum
  API->>API: Calcule prix menu + livraison
  API->>SQL: Cree commande status pending
  API->>SQL: Decremente stock menu
  API->>SMTP: Envoie confirmation
  API-->>UI: Retour commande + total
  UI-->>C: Confirmation visuelle
